    NeedUsbDebugBody = @(
        'ADB connection setup is needed.'
        ''
        'How to enable USB debugging on a Samsung phone:'
        '1. Unlock the phone.'
        '2. Go to Settings > About phone > Software information.'
        '3. Tap "Build number" seven times to enable Developer options.'
        '4. Go back to Settings and open Developer options.'
        '5. Turn on "USB debugging".'
        '6. Reconnect the USB cable and switch the USB mode to "File transfer" if possible.'
        '7. On the phone, approve the "Allow USB debugging?" prompt and check "Always allow from this computer".'
        ''
        'If the prompt does not appear:'
        '- Unplug and reconnect the cable.'
        '- Turn USB debugging off and on again in Developer options.'
        '- Run adb kill-server on the PC and try again.'
        '- Make sure the phone screen is on and unlocked.'
    )
